<p>Cerca del apartamento hay paradas de autobuses; de la l&iacute;nea 109 (Črnomerec-Dugave; que conecta el noroeste y el suroeste de la ciudad), y la l&iacute;nea 118 (Trg Mažuraničevih-Voltino; que conecta al este y el oeste de la ciudad &ndash; es la forma m&aacute;s r&aacute;pida de llegar al centro !en diez minutos!), tambien paradas de tranv&iacute;a (cinco minutos a pie) de la l&iacute;nea 2, 6, 11 y l&iacute;nea nocturna 31</p>

<h3>Desde la estaci&oacute;n central de autobuses</h3>

<p>Desde&quot;&nbsp; la terminal de autobuses (Držićeva ulica) pueden llegar al apartamento directamente en tranv&iacute;a (l&iacute;nea 2 y 6) direcci&oacute;n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\&quot;Črnomerec\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\&quot;. Este trayecto dura de quince a veinte minutos. Hay que bajarse en la estaci&oacute;n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\&quot;Sveti Duh\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\&quot;(pen&uacute;ltima de la l&iacute;nea), y se tiene que andar cinco minutos a pie por la calle &bdquo;Selska cesta&ldquo; hasta el apartamento.</p>

<h3>Desde la estaci&oacute;n principal de trenes</h3>

<p>La estaci&oacute;n de tren est&aacute; a s&oacute;lo tres paradas de tranv&iacute;a desde la terminal central de autobuses. Por eso se pueden utilizar las mismas l&iacute;neas de tranv&iacute;a (2 y 6) direcci&oacute;n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\&quot;Črnomerec\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\&quot;. La parada de tranv&iacute;a est&aacute; delante de la estaci&oacute;n de tren. Hay que bajarse en la estaci&oacute;n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\&quot;Sveti Duh\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\&quot; (pen&uacute;ltima), y hay que andar cinco minutos a pie por la calle &bdquo;Selska cesta&ldquo; hasta el apartamento.</p>

<h3>Desde el aeropuerto</h3>

